<title>INDIA: India's RBI repo auctions calendar for May.</title>
<headline>India's RBI repo auctions calendar for May.</headline>
<dateline>BOMBAY 1997-04-24</dateline>
<text>
<p>The Reserve Bank of India (RBI) on Thursday announced the schedule for repo auctions in May.</p>
<p>The repo auctions will be open to parties holding SGL account and current account with the RBI.</p>
<p>The following are the details of the auction.</p>
<p>.</p>
<p>Date of auction  Date of payment   Period  Repurchase date</p>
<p>-----------------------------------------------------------</p>
<p>April    25	April    26	 4 days  April    30</p>
<p>April    29	April    30	 3 days  May	 3</p>
<p>May	 2	May	 3	 4 days  May	 7</p>
<p>May	 6	May	 7	 3 days  May	10</p>
<p>May	 9	May	10	 4 days  May	14</p>
<p>May	13	May	14	 3 days  May	17</p>
<p>May	16	May	17	 4 days  May	21</p>
<p>May	20	May	21	 3 days  May	24</p>
<p>May	23	May	24	 4 days  May	28</p>
<p>May	27	May	28	 3 days  May	31</p>
<p>May	30	May	31	 3 days  June	3</p>
<p>-- Bombay newsroom +91-22-265 9000</p>
